name: The last day of summer.
description:
Nothing I am, nothing I dream, nothing is new. Nothing I think or believe in or say. Nothing is true. All that I have, all that I hold - all that is wrong. All that I feel for or trust in or love - all that is gone... It used to be so easy, I never even tried. Yeah, it used to be so easy... But the last day of summer, never felt so cold. The last day of summer, never felt so old. The last day of summer, never felt so cold... Never felt so...

Oil on canvas.
